---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Gear — Metro Tacoma Fencing Club"
  description="MTFC gear and equipment guide. Shop MTFC branded apparel or learn what you need to start fencing."
>
  <!-- Page header -->
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="header-blade"></div>
      <div class="epee-accent" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 200 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" class="epee-svg">
          <line x1="100" y1="580" x2="100" y2="80" stroke="#00e085" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.3"/>
          <ellipse cx="100" cy="80" rx="30" ry="16" stroke="#00e085" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity="0.4"/>
          <rect x="92" y="96" width="16" height="50" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="#1a6b5f" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4"/>
          <ellipse cx="100" cy="152" rx="12" ry="8" stroke="#1a6b5f" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Shop &amp; Gear</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">MTFC Gear</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Section 1: MTFC Branded Clothing -->
  <section class="section shop-section" aria-labelledby="shop-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Shop</span>
        <h2 id="shop-heading">MTFC Branded Clothing</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="coming-soon-card">
        <h3 class="coming-soon-heading">Coming Soon</h3>
        <p class="coming-soon-text">Our merch store is being updated — check back soon for MTFC branded apparel and accessories.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Gear Basics -->
  <section class="section gear-section" aria-labelledby="equipment-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Equipment</span>
        <h2 id="equipment-heading">What You Need to Fence</h2>
      </div>

      <p class="gear-intro">
        To fence safely you need four pieces of equipment: a mask, a jacket, a glove, and a weapon (foil or épée). All four must meet USA Fencing standards.
      </p>

      <div class="gear-list">
        <div class="gear-item">
          <h3 class="gear-item-title">Mask</h3>
          <p class="gear-item-desc">Full-head protection with mesh front. FIE or USFA rated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gear-item">
          <h3 class="gear-item-title">Jacket</h3>
          <p class="gear-item-desc">Padded fencing jacket covering torso and sword arm.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gear-item">
          <h3 class="gear-item-title">Glove</h3>
          <p class="gear-item-desc">Single glove for the sword hand.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gear-item">
          <h3 class="gear-item-title">Weapon</h3>
          <p class="gear-item-desc">Foil or épée with a practice tip (not sharp).</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="gear-closing">
        Don't have gear yet? Loaner equipment is available for your first session. <a href="/classes/new-to-fencing">See our New to Fencing page</a> to get started.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Page header ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .page-header {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-20) 0 var(--space-16);
    background: var(--color-bg-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .page-header-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .header-blade {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1.5px;
    height: 200%;
    top: -50%;
    right: 18%;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(0, 224, 133, 0.2), transparent);
    transform: rotate(-30deg);
  }

  .epee-accent {
    position: absolute;
    right: 8%;
    top: 0;
    height: 100%;
    width: 200px;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .epee-svg {
    height: 100%;
    width: auto;
  }

  .page-header .section-label {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .page-title {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-white);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  /* ── Section 1: Shop ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .shop-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .coming-soon-card {
    background: var(--color-navy);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-10);
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .coming-soon-heading {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .coming-soon-text {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── Section 2: Gear Basics ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .gear-section {
    background: var(--color-gray-100);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .gear-intro {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .gear-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .gear-list {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .gear-item {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .gear-item-title {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .gear-item-desc {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .gear-closing {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .gear-closing a {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-navy);
    transition: color var(--transition-base);
  }

  .gear-closing a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
